10
00:01:50,120 --> 00:01:51,440
You risked your life
to break into the palace

11
00:01:51,440 --> 00:01:52,600
and take me
from the Crown Prince Mansion.

12
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:54,400
What exactly are your intentions?

13
00:01:55,400 --> 00:01:56,120
Yin,

14
00:01:56,240 --> 00:01:57,360
I promised you

15
00:01:57,720 --> 00:01:58,840
I wouldn't leave you.

16
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:02,240
Even if it's the depths of hell,

17
00:02:02,440 --> 00:02:03,680
I'll break in

18
00:02:04,080 --> 00:02:05,280
and fight our way out together.

19
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:08,640
Yin,

20
00:02:09,280 --> 00:02:10,720
Li Chi confused your memory,

21
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:12,120
but in that critical moment

22
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:13,560
you still chose to believe me.

23
00:02:14,520 --> 00:02:15,480
I'm very happy.

24
00:02:20,200 --> 00:02:21,480
I don't believe what he says

25
00:02:23,040 --> 00:02:24,360
and I don't believe what you say either.

26
00:02:24,920 --> 00:02:26,240
I want to recover

27
00:02:26,720 --> 00:02:28,200
my own memory.

28
00:02:35,480 --> 00:02:36,280
Fine,

29
00:02:36,640 --> 00:02:37,440
I'll be with you.

30
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:46,960
This is...

31
00:02:47,480 --> 00:02:48,320
The Preceptor Mansion,

32
00:02:49,280 --> 00:02:50,320
our home.

33
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:07,920
How could this be?

34
00:03:08,480 --> 00:03:10,160
Was what Xiao Zhi said true?

35
00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:15,680
Madam Xie,

36
00:03:16,200 --> 00:03:17,080
here's the marriage certificate.

37
00:03:18,480 --> 00:03:19,760
Here's the dagger you used

38
00:03:20,200 --> 00:03:21,960
to try to kill the master
on your wedding day.

39
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:23,880
Here's the poison

40
00:03:24,520 --> 00:03:25,920
you used to coat the dagger.

41
00:03:27,080 --> 00:03:28,200
And this pomegranate wine

42
00:03:29,720 --> 00:03:31,400
was laced with aphrodisiac.

43
00:03:33,040 --> 00:03:33,840
Wait,

44
00:03:34,320 --> 00:03:36,080
why would I use this on him?

45
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:37,720
To kill him, of course.

46
00:03:40,840 --> 00:03:41,640
By the way,

47
00:03:43,720 --> 00:03:45,680
Madam Xie, do you remember these?

48
00:03:50,560 --> 00:03:51,800
I did this to him too?

49
