You didn't.

50
00:03:54,080 --> 00:03:55,480
But the scars

51
00:03:55,480 --> 00:03:56,880
were caused because of you.

52
00:03:56,880 --> 00:03:57,680
Xiao Zhi.

53
00:04:03,760 --> 00:04:04,360
Yin,

54
00:04:04,600 --> 00:04:05,760
have you remembered something?

55
00:04:08,720 --> 00:04:10,200
If I married you,

56
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:11,480
