57
00:04:12,640 --> 00:04:14,880
You were already engaged to Li Chi.

58
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:16,600
It was I who forcibly married you.

59
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:22,000
You were defiled by that villain.

60
00:04:23,520 --> 00:04:24,400
You were so heartbroken,

61
00:04:24,400 --> 00:04:25,520
washing your face with tears every day

62
00:04:26,200 --> 00:04:27,240
and waiting for me to rescue you.

63
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:30,160
He said I was humiliated by you

64
00:04:30,160 --> 00:04:31,080
