65
00:04:34,560 --> 00:04:36,080
It's one thing to deceive you

66
00:04:36,200 --> 00:04:37,880
but how did he deceive himself as well?

67
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:40,560
He doesn't know you at all.

68
00:04:45,920 --> 00:04:46,920
