I've always been sincere with you.

72
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:55,360
I never thought about,

73
00:04:55,360 --> 00:04:56,080
nor would I dare

74
00:04:56,400 --> 00:04:57,240
to humiliate you.

75
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:04,440
My master never

76
00:05:04,440 --> 00:05:06,200
had any disrespectful intentions
toward you.

77
00:05:06,800 --> 00:05:07,560
However...

78
00:05:11,080 --> 00:05:12,200
Given what happened,

79
00:05:12,640 --> 00:05:14,480
it's understandable you misunderstood.

80
00:05:14,640 --> 00:05:15,440
Xiao Zhi,

81
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:17,280
you may leave.

82
00:05:20,080 --> 00:05:22,400
I'll take my leave now.

83
00:05:26,880 --> 00:05:27,680
Wait.

84
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:37,560
Aside from the memory loss,

85
00:05:37,640 --> 00:05:38,800
does Yin have any other injuries?

86
00:05:39,640 --> 00:05:41,240
For now, it seems to be
only memory loss.

87
00:05:41,520 --> 00:05:43,800
However, there might be
long-term effects.

88
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:46,640
But since I'm not skilled in this area,

89
00:05:46,920 --> 00:05:49,320
we may need Ms. Ruolan's help.

90
00:05:52,840 --> 00:05:53,640
Go ahead.

91
00:06:02,920 --> 00:06:04,120
Why are you looking at me like that?

92
00:06:05,960 --> 00:06:06,760
And then?

93
00:06:08,120 --> 00:06:09,000
What do you mean?

94
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:11,840
What happened
after I failed to kill you?

95
00:06:14,240 --> 00:06:15,200
And then

96
00:06:16,080 --> 00:06:17,400
you fell in love with me.

97
00:06:18,560 --> 00:06:20,040
Words alone aren't enough.

98
00:06:24,400 --> 00:06:26,120
I haven't regained my memory yet.
What are you doing?

99
00:06:29,120 --> 00:06:30,040
You've forgotten,

100
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:31,680
so let's start over.

101
00:06:37,360 --> 00:06:39,720
I'm an overbearing

102
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:41,320
and unprincipled villain.

103
00:06:42,880 --> 00:06:45,680
I don't care about rituals or virtues,

104
00:06:45,800 --> 00:06:46,840
rules or propriety.

105
00:06:48,160 --> 00:06:49,160
This is the person

106
00:06:49,480 --> 00:06:50,960
you're in love with.

107
00:06:55,380 --> 00:06:57,550
♪The scholarly spirit♪

108
00:06:57,990 --> 00:07:00,160
♪Remains the same
after the rise and fall♪

109
00:07:00,820 --> 00:07:04,800
♪As I observe the scroll,
the world's affairs come into view♪

110
00:07:06,200 --> 00:07:09,350
♪The sharpness of the pen
cuts through the gloom♪

111
00:07:09,380 --> 00:07:12,160
♪This paper only sees black and white♪

112
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:14,160
[Na Family Ancestral Hall]

113
00:07:14,160 --> 00:07:17,620
♪Whose heart
splits it apart persistently♪

114
00:07:18,300 --> 00:07:19,520
♪Lift your gaze♪

115
00:07:19,870 --> 00:07:23,880
♪Behold the myriad forms of life
beyond the study♪

116
00:07:24,010 --> 00:07:25,520
♪Tears stain the thin paper♪

117
00:07:25,710 --> 00:07:28,890
♪Glimpsing the sorrow
when leaving words behind♪

118
00:07:29,440 --> 00:07:32,500
♪Now searching for the chapters♪

119
00:07:32,930 --> 00:07:35,360
♪In the clear moonlight,
dreams lie beyond the clouds♪

120
00:07:35,590 --> 00:07:37,290
♪In the unknown places♪

121
00:07:37,710 --> 00:07:41,050
♪Resting in silence, awaiting♪

122
00:07:41,410 --> 00:07:45,200
♪On worn inscriptions, the rites endure
beneath the setting sun♪

123
00:07:45,560 --> 00:07:47,440
♪The sage reveres from afar♪

124
00:07:47,950 --> 00:07:48,950
♪The three stone steles♪

125
00:07:49,280 --> 00:07:50,080
Yin,

126
00:07:51,400 --> 00:07:52,800
did you remember something?

127
00:07:55,960 --> 00:07:56,800
No.

128
00:08:03,240 --> 00:08:06,000
No, but compared to
that self-righteous hypocrite Li Chi,

129
00:08:06,120 --> 00:08:08,960
a straightforwardly villain like you
is much more to my taste.

130
00:08:13,280 --> 00:08:13,760
Yin,

131
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:15,200
let me take you somewhere.

132
00:08:15,640 --> 00:08:17,520
We'll recover your memories.

133
00:08:26,840 --> 00:08:27,960
Where is this place?

134
00:08:28,560 --> 00:08:29,720
A place to treat your mind.

135
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:33,200
I don't have mental issues.

136
00:08:52,880 --> 00:08:53,560
How is she?

137
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:56,880
There are many ways to make someone
lose their memory.

138
00:08:57,480 --> 00:08:58,520
It's hard to investigate.

139
00:08:59,200 --> 00:09:01,200
Do you have any other clues?

140
00:09:01,840 --> 00:09:02,800
If you ask me,

141
00:09:04,120 --> 00:09:05,560
this is the second time
she's lost her memory.

142
00:09:05,880 --> 00:09:06,760
Twice?

143
00:09:06,760 --> 00:09:07,560
Yes,

144
00:09:08,600 --> 00:09:10,600
this time, she lost all her memories.

145
00:09:11,120 --> 00:09:11,920
Last time,

146
00:09:12,160 --> 00:09:14,760
certain fragments
of her memory were replaced.

147
00:09:15,520 --> 00:09:16,560
Memory replacement?

148
00:09:18,480 --> 00:09:20,080
That's quite unusual.

149
00:09:21,920 --> 00:09:23,840
After your memory was replaced,

150
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:25,720
did your face show any changes?

151
00:09:30,160 --> 00:09:31,400
I don't remember anything.

152
00:09:33,200 --> 00:09:34,000
Her face...

153
00:09:36,840 --> 00:09:37,880
I remember

154
00:09:38,880 --> 00:09:40,040
when she was young,

155
00:09:43,920 --> 00:09:45,880
there was a red mole here.

156
00:09:48,920 --> 00:09:49,840
Blood Reversing the Meridians.

157
00:09:50,480 --> 00:09:51,320
Blood Reversing the Meridians?

158
00:09:52,640 --> 00:09:53,680
I know what this is.

159
00:10:00,560 --> 00:10:01,440
Master, look.

160
00:10:02,560 --> 00:10:04,120
This is a secret art
from the Southern Regions,

161
00:10:04,720 --> 00:10:06,280
where memories are sealed

162
00:10:06,800 --> 00:10:08,320
or even altered using poison needles.

163
00:10:08,520 --> 00:10:09,880
This art is extremely dangerous.

164
00:10:11,360 --> 00:10:14,160
The first time, it causes
Blood Reversing the Meridians

165
00:10:14,360 --> 00:10:15,360
and confusion in memory.

166
00:10:16,040 --> 00:10:18,160
The second time results
in total memory loss.

167
00:10:18,760 --> 00:10:20,160
If used a third time,

168
00:10:20,400 --> 00:10:22,320
the person will become
a complete idiot.

169
00:10:28,760 --> 00:10:30,080
How can this be undone?

170
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:33,040
First, suck out the poison needle

171
00:10:33,320 --> 00:10:35,280
and then use acupuncture
to regulate the blood.

172
00:10:36,080 --> 00:10:37,000
Master, what do you think?

173
00:10:37,320 --> 00:10:38,120
I'll do it.

174
00:10:43,960 --> 00:10:44,760
Don't worry.

175
00:10:45,280 --> 00:10:46,600
My dear, I'll be very gentle.

176
00:10:49,680 --> 00:10:50,800
I was just thinking,

177
00:10:50,800 --> 00:10:52,160
am I trusting you

178
00:10:52,200 --> 00:10:53,200
too easily?

179
00:10:53,600 --> 00:10:55,360
If you were to harm me on purpose,

180
00:10:55,520 --> 00:10:57,320
wouldn't I be putting my life
in your hands?

181
00:11:00,240 --> 00:11:01,280
My dear, rest assured.

182
00:11:01,280 --> 00:11:02,760
Even if it costs my life,

183
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:04,520
I'll protect you.

184
00:11:10,200 --> 00:11:13,450
♪In old age, we speak of fervent love♪

185
00:11:13,810 --> 00:11:17,390
♪The years and seasons have burned us♪

186
00:11:17,390 --> 00:11:19,390
♪What I fear most
is rain falling into my eyes♪

187
00:11:19,500 --> 00:11:22,390
♪Too many things are hard to conceal♪

188
00:11:22,720 --> 00:11:25,610
♪Brewed into tears♪

189
00:11:25,980 --> 00:11:27,780
♪He, with no time to spare, should be♪

190
00:11:27,810 --> 00:11:29,960
♪Grass and trees, untouched by harm♪

191
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:33,970
♪Yet he ventured into the tumult
of the world, taking a journey♪

192
00:11:34,200 --> 00:11:37,990
♪He, like the moon falling to the dust,
full of desolation♪

193
00:11:41,640 --> 00:11:42,200
Yin,

194
00:11:42,800 --> 00:11:43,560
how are you feeling?

195
00:11:43,560 --> 00:11:46,710
♪Love, hate, joy, sorrow,
he dares not taste again♪

196
00:11:51,040 --> 00:11:51,600
Yin.

197
00:11:51,600 --> 00:11:54,980
♪Witnessing the fleeting affairs
of the world♪

198
00:11:55,460 --> 00:11:58,350
♪Too barren♪

199
00:11:58,440 --> 00:11:59,000
Yin.

200
00:11:59,770 --> 00:12:01,570
♪He, with no time to spare, should be♪

201
00:12:01,770 --> 00:12:03,900
♪Grass and trees, untouched by harm♪

202
00:12:05,360 --> 00:12:05,880
Yin,

203
00:12:06,480 --> 00:12:07,040
it's fine.

204
00:12:07,280 --> 00:12:08,320
If you can't remember,

205
00:12:08,520 --> 00:12:09,440
take your time.

206
00:12:09,440 --> 00:12:11,440
♪He's like the moon falling
into the dust, full of desolation♪

207
00:12:15,880 --> 00:12:18,720
This secret art that affects memory
can only be used twice.

208
00:12:18,720 --> 00:12:19,400
The first time,

209
00:12:19,600 --> 00:12:21,840
Your Highness used it
to alter her childhood memories.

210
00:12:22,080 --> 00:12:22,800
This art is dangerous.

211
00:12:23,120 --> 00:12:24,720
Are you sure you want to use it again?

212
00:12:25,400 --> 00:12:26,640
Dangerous or not,

213
00:12:28,080 --> 00:12:29,960
as long as it keeps her by my side.

214
00:12:29,960 --> 00:12:32,450
♪Too barren♪

215
00:12:33,400 --> 00:12:33,960
Don't be afraid,

216
00:12:34,240 --> 00:12:34,800
Yin.

217
00:12:37,200 --> 00:12:38,200
When you wake up,

218
00:12:39,080 --> 00:12:41,160
we can start over.

219
00:12:52,880 --> 00:12:53,920
Yin, it's OK.

220
00:12:54,520 --> 00:12:55,600
Just rest for now.

221
00:12:55,600 --> 00:12:56,600
I'll go get your medicine.

222
00:13:04,440 --> 00:13:06,460
♪Speaking of love and hate♪

223
00:13:07,080 --> 00:13:09,590
♪How can I distinguish them?♪

224
00:13:11,320 --> 00:13:13,850
♪Longing for fate, praying sincerely♪

225
00:13:14,170 --> 00:13:17,090
♪Yet the world does not acknowledge it♪

226
00:13:17,960 --> 00:13:19,120
It's been so many years.

227
00:13:19,200 --> 00:13:20,520
Why did you come so late?

228
00:13:21,080 --> 00:13:22,640
Why did it take you so long to find me?

229
00:13:27,440 --> 00:13:28,240
Yin,

230
00:13:29,200 --> 00:13:30,600
you remember everything now?

231
00:13:32,200 --> 00:13:32,720
Yin.

232
00:13:32,730 --> 00:13:34,730
♪Fireworks fall like rain♪

233
00:13:35,060 --> 00:13:38,120
♪But soon they cool♪

234
00:13:38,120 --> 00:13:40,000
Yin, does it still hurt?

235
00:13:40,000 --> 00:13:42,000
♪I look, adding a few more strokes
to the word "love"♪

236
00:13:43,520 --> 00:13:45,680
After all these years,
you still haven't learned a thing.

237
00:13:45,920 --> 00:13:47,560
You look so fierce and bad

238
00:13:48,000 --> 00:13:49,600
yet you get bullied everywhere,

239
00:13:51,320 --> 00:13:52,880
ending up covered in wounds.

240
00:13:54,880 --> 00:13:55,680
How foolish.

241
00:13:55,680 --> 00:13:57,460
♪I sigh, why are you and I♪

242
00:13:58,600 --> 00:13:59,560
So what?

243
00:14:02,640 --> 00:14:03,640
After all these years,

244
00:14:04,840 --> 00:14:06,480
I still made my way to your side.

245
00:14:58,960 --> 00:14:59,760
She's resting?

246
00:15:00,200 --> 00:15:00,760
Yes.

247
00:15:03,440 --> 00:15:06,280
