248
00:15:08,120 --> 00:15:09,200
She's no longer in any danger.

249
00:15:09,920 --> 00:15:11,920
You should be more concerned
about yourself.

250
00:15:12,600 --> 00:15:13,400
Me?

251
00:15:14,560 --> 00:15:16,200
You're carrying
the Summer Withering poison.

252
00:15:16,520 --> 00:15:17,960
